nodes.text: Captain Terrae Lekes was a small-time starship thief operating in the Minos Cluster by 4 ABY. The Galactic Empire had placed a bounty on Lekes, which was processed through the Goa-Ato, the Rodian hunters' guild. The Guild Assignments Group, considering the capture of Lekes to be an easy task, assigned the bounty to Teksli Yenak, a hunter from the Rodian Chattza Clan with a less-than-impressive reputation.
